PN,43201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774353808
OL,3,CCornish satellite to play role in
OL,4,CNASA's first manned lunar mission in
OL,5,C54 years
OL,7,FA satellite on Cornwall's Lizard
OL,8,FPeninsula will be used to track the
OL,9,Fworld's first manned lunar mission in
OL,10,Fmore than half a century.
OL,12,FStaff at Goonhilly Earth Station say
OL,13,Fthey hope their role in NASA's Artemis
OL,14,FII mission will secure Cornwall's
OL,15,Ffuture involvement in space missions
OL,16,Fto the Moon and Mars.
OL,18,FArtemis II will send four astronauts
OL,19,Fon a ten-day round trip around the
OL,20,FMoon and back.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
