OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774353808
OL,3,CCornish satellite to play role in
OL,4,CNASA's first manned lunar mission in
OL,5,C54 years
OL,7,FIt's the first time humans will return
OL,8,Fto the Moon since Apollo 17 in 1972,
OL,9,Fand will see the first woman and black
OL,10,Fastronaut travel beyond low Earth
OL,11,Forbit.
OL,13,F"Four people going round the Moon is
OL,14,Fquite a big deal, so it feels kind of
OL,15,Fstrange that you can be sat down on
OL,16,Fthe Lizard looking at a computer
OL,17,Fscreen seeing that data come back.
OL,18,FIt's really exciting," said Ollie
OL,19,FHancock, mission operations engineer.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774353808
OL,3,CCornish satellite to play role in
OL,4,CNASA's first manned lunar mission in
OL,5,C54 years
OL,7,FGoonhilly's satellite, called Merlin,
OL,8,Funderwent an #8million refurbishment
OL,9,Fin 2019 and is currently being used to
OL,10,Ftrack a spacecraft orbiting Mars.
OL,12,FIt is the world's first privately-
OL,13,Fowned lunar and deep-space
OL,14,Fcommunications antenna and in 2022 it
OL,15,Fprovided communication and tracking
OL,16,Fsupport for the unmanned Artemis I
OL,17,Fmission to the Moon.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774353808
OL,3,CCornish satellite to play role in
OL,4,CNASA's first manned lunar mission in
OL,5,C54 years
OL,7,F"We're going to show how sensitive
OL,8,Fthis antenna is. We've got all the
OL,9,Ftiming systems, all the procedures,
OL,10,Fall the team are well versed and well
OL,11,Frehearsed," said Matthew Cosby,
OL,12,Fdirector of space engineering.
OL,14,F"We'll show the full capability of
OL,15,Fwhat we can do, and we're using
OL,16,FArtemis II as an example. Then, when
OL,17,Fwe actually see people walking on the
OL,18,FMoon, we'll be part of that if we are
OL,19,Fsuccessful in our qualification."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
